    <item>
      <title>[부음] 백성문 법무법인 아리율 대표변호사 별세 외   </title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/11/01/IJB3MIIXUFGXXGKBOQS6KAJI4E/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/11/01/IJB3MIIXUFGXXGKBOQS6KAJI4E/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Oct 2025 15:52:00 +0000</pubDate>
